che Tiefenschärfe. Beiträge von Hans Günter Hockerts, Christiane Kuller, Lutz Leisering, Christian Marschallek, Wilfried Rudloff, Winfried Süß, Cornelius Torp  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a FA license: uhttps://www.degruyter.com/dg/page/free-access-policy uhttps://www.degruyter.com/dg/page/open-access-policy  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 28. Feb 2023) 0aEqualityxSocial aspectsvCongresses. 0aWelfare statevCongresses. 4aDeutschland. 4aGroßbritannien. 4aSozialstaat. 7aBUSINESS & ECONOMICS / Economics / General.2bisacsh1 aHockerts, Hans Günter, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHockerts, Hans Günter, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aKuller, Christiane, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLeisering, Lutz, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMarschallek, Christian, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRudloff, Wilfried, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSüß, Winfried, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSüß, Winfried, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aTorp, Cornelius, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Business and Economics 2000 - 2014z9783110635737oZDB-23-GBE08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruyterteBook-Paket OWV/AV  Geschichte 2005-2012z9783110346787oZDB-23-OGS0 cprintz978348659176740uhttps://doi.org/10.1524/9783486708271zOpen Access7040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783486708271zOpen Access70423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783486708271/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-GBEc2000d